  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的数据流转图，核心是成绩同步模块GradeSync，它要先把数据推送给课堂服务ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，GradeSync作为起点。那ClassroomService之后数据流向哪里？是直接到学生数据库，还是先经过其他中间层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ClassroomService处理完后，会把整合好的课程数据推送到LMS Portal，这是我们的学习管理门户。然后LMS Portal再回流到另一个ClassroomService实例做二次处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：第二个ClassroomService和第一个是同一个服务节点吗？还是不同的部署实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是不同的实例，但用同样的服务名，你可以理解为区域A的ClassroomService推给Portal，Portal再回调区域B的ClassroomService做最终持久化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我按从左到右布局：GradeSync → ClassroomService → LMS Portal → ClassroomService → StudentDB。最后一个节点是StudentDB对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，最终落到StudentDB。整个链路是GradeSync启动同步，经过两层ClassroomService和一层Portal，最后入库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，五个节点按LR横向排列。检查一下：GradeSync在最左，StudentDB在最右，中间两次经过ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——第二个ClassroomService到StudentDB之间，我漏了一个环节。实际上Portal回调ClassroomService后，是直接写StudentDB，但中间没有别的节点了。你现在的图是对的，但我描述有误，确认无误。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，当前链路保持：GradeSync → ClassroomService → LMS Portal → ClassroomService → StudentDB。没有遗漏节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "另外，能否在图上标注一下，第一个ClassroomService是\"课程数据预处理\"，第二个是\"最终入库校验\"？虽然服务名相同，但阶段不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Mermaid里节点显示名称可以自定义，但ID必须唯一。现在两个ClassroomService用了相同ID，会冲突。需要把第二个改成ClassroomService_B或者类似区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，内部区分一下，对外展示还是ClassroomService。图能表达清楚流向就行，最终版本就这样定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
